OL,3,CMum-of-three tried to take her own
OL,4,Clife after traumatic birth
OL,6,FLaura shared her story with ITV
OL,7,FGranada Reports.
OL,9,FA mum-of-three who tried to take her
OL,10,Fown life days after giving birth to
OL,11,Fher son is calling for more awareness
OL,12,Faround birth trauma.
OL,14,FLaura Crawshaw, 37, from Whitefield,
OL,15,Fhad three traumatic births over the
OL,16,Fspace of 10 years and was left with
OL,17,FPost Traumatic Stress Disorder (PTSD).
