OL,3,CMum-of-three tried to take her own
OL,4,Clife after traumatic birth
OL,6,FIt comes as an all-party parliamentary
OL,7,Finquiry into the issue is launched,
OL,8,Fwith thousands of people already
OL,9,Fsubmitting written and oral evidence.
OL,11,FDuring Laura's first pregnancy with
OL,12,Fher son Kayden, she suffered a life-
OL,13,Fthreatening placental abruption at 35
OL,14,Fweeks and needed an emergency C-
OL,15,Fsection.
OL,17,F"The midwives helped me through the
OL,18,Fworst three minutes of my life", she
OL,19,Fsaid. "It took six minutes to bleed
OL,20,Fout, one hour to stitch me back up."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/14
