OL,6,F"The NHS is in crisis": Rachael
OL,7,FMcGrath speaks to Granada Reports
OL,8,Fpresenters Lucy Meacock and Andy
OL,9,FBonner about the public inquiry into
OL,10,Fbirth trauma
OL,12,FRachael McGrath, the chair of Birth
OL,13,FTrauma Association, believes the
OL,14,Freason why some women experience
OL,15,Ftraumatic births is because the "NHS
OL,16,Fis in crisis".
OL,18,FShe said and the health service is
OL,19,Fstruggling to maintain maternity staff
OL,20,Fand "therefore services are getting
OL,21,Fmore difficult to provide."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/14
