OL,3,CMum-of-three tried to take her own
OL,4,Clife after traumatic birth
OL,6,F"Women are coming into hospitals and
OL,7,Fasking for pain relief and there's no
OL,8,Fone there to administer it - and this
OL,9,Fis all helping to embed trauma",
OL,10,FRachel said.
OL,12,FShe continued to say that the
OL,13,Fparliamentary inquiry has "opened
OL,14,FPandora's box" of years of birth
OL,15,Ftrauma events.
OL,17,F"An 84-year-old lady wrote in. She had
OL,18,Fa C-section more than 60 years ago
OL,19,Fwithout adequate anesthetic and has
OL,20,Fnever recovered."
