OL,6,FMeanwhile, Rachel, who joined the BTA
OL,7,Fafter experiencing birth trauma, says
OL,8,Fsome women are terminating pregnancies
OL,9,Fbecause of distressing experiences
OL,10,Fthey have had in the past.
OL,12,FShe said: "Nobody wants to make that
OL,13,Fdecision."
OL,15,FAn NHS spokesperson said: "The NHS is
OL,16,Fimproving our support to women who
OL,17,Fhave experienced a traumatic birth
OL,18,Fthrough rolling out specialist
OL,19,Fcommunity perinatal teams and offering
OL,20,Fcomprehensive postnatal check-ups.
